title: Winning numbers drawn in 'DC 5 Midday' game

maintext:
WASHINGTON (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Dist. of Columbia Lottery’s “DC 5 Midday” game were:
1-5-2-5-4
(one, five, two, five, four)
